* Iron Raptor rushed out of the Ark, the shields were failing and she was 
loosing her temper!
She snarled and looked around, she saw Rampage but saw that Liono and a few 
others had it under control...or so it seemed.
Iron Raptor looked at the shields and saw a wed over it, draining their 
power.
She then turned to Hell Beast and snarled, she was sick and tired of the 
Predacons attacking and it would only be reasonable to attack them at the 
source!
Iron Raptor ran a few feet from the ship and fired her splatter gun at Hell 
Beast, as she did so she almost knew for sure that she would have to use her 
second beast mode, eventually.
She then pulled out her sword and pointed it towards the Predacon 
commander...*

" You may have just sealed your fate by attacking us, Predacon!"
